a global automotive company united by a single purpose to earn customersfor life earning customers for life is the foundational promise of general motors it is a commitment to treat every customer with respect to care about a customer not just when they purchase a new vehicle but for as long as they own the vehicle appreciating customers and fighting every day to earn their loyalty inspires us to make better safer higher value cars trucks and crossovers our people general motors employs the finest workforce in the automotive world we are a richly diverse and dedicated team  employees we serve continents  global headquarters detroit michigan usa across timezones  and we speak languages  our brands from electric cars to heavyduty fullsize trucks general motors provides a complete range of vehicles that meets the needs and expectations of drivers on a truly global scale there are  distinctive automotive brands under the general motors corporate umbrella chevrolet buick gmc cadillac opel vauxhall holden baojun wuling and jiefang chevrolet an innovative range of awardwinning affordable and fuelefficient cars trucks and suvs all delivering firstclass refinement in every detail from design performance and technology in mind learn more at chevroletcom  chevrolet bolt ev buick awardwinning modern luxury sedans and crossovers marrying sculpted design fuelefficiency spirited performance and advanced technology it’s luxury as it should be your kind of luxury learn more at buickcom  buick lacrosse gmc purposebuilt vehicles reaching a higher standard through engineering excellence and innovation we give our customers the power to be their best we are professional grade learn more at gmccom  gmc acadia cadillac the bold daring and original cadillac lineup seamlessly blends driving dynamics refinement and technology to satisfy enthusiasts and luxury seekers alike learn more at cadillaccom  cadillac xt crossover holden one of only seven fully integrated global general motors operati